### Basic Case Statements

Currently running through a sprint to learn the intermediate/advanced SQL concepts. 

Expression: CASE
Clauses: WHEN, THEN, ELSE, END

# Examples

```
CASE WHEN x = 1 THEN 'a'
     WHEN x = 2 THEN 'b'
     ELSE 'c' END AS new_column

or

```
CASE WHEN x = 1 THEN 'a'
     WHEN x = 2 THEN 'b'
     ELSE 'c' 
END AS new_column

